cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR 

The paper deals with multi-modal classification using images and text descriptions, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of deep neural networks for this task also suggests machine learning (cs.LG) as a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves feature representation learning, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
